<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-04-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-04-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="15" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d15">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">Hopkins Papers: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Prime Minister <persName type="from">Churchill</persName> to the President’s Special
                                    Assistant</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Hopkins</hi></persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d15fn1">Channel
                                    of transmission not indicated.</note>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-04-11">April 11, 1943</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>I cannot help being much disappointed by your telegram.</p>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>